author: slessard
msg: TRINIDAD-135 Add a non-final getPartialTriggers(FacesBean) to XhtmlRenderer to allow easier customization. Specifically this allow to have shoudRenderId return true whenever the component has partialTriggers that may not be stored in the partialTriggers property itself.
